<sect1 id="COLOUR_1notes-131_1s1"><sect2 id="COLOUR_1notes-131_1s2"><sect3 id="COLOUR_1notes-131_1s3"><sect4 id="COLOUR_1notes-131_1s4"><sect5 id="COLOUR_1notes-131">
<title>Notes</title><para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Applies to <bold>text output</bold> (e.g., <computeroutput>PRINT</computeroutput>). <linebreak/>
</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>The setting affects subsequent text until changed again. <linebreak/>
</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>For <bold>background</bold> colour, use <ref refid="BACKGROUND" kindref="compound">BACKGROUND</ref>.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>For <bold>graphics drawing colours</bold>, use <ref refid="GCOL" kindref="compound">GCOL</ref>.</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para><bold>See also:</bold> <ref refid="BACKGROUND" kindref="compound">BACKGROUND</ref>, <ref refid="GCOL" kindref="compound">GCOL</ref> </para>
